why skip connection works:
it is easier to learn a residual function, than a brand new mapping
假如优化目标函数是逼近一个恒等映射, 而不是0映射， 那么学习找到对恒等映射的扰动会比重新学习一个映射函数要容易。从下图可以看出，残差函数一般会有较小的响应波动，表明恒等映射是一个合理的预处理。


increase performance without learnng new parameters


building block 到 bottleneck block
building block 和 bottleneck block have similar time complexity


34 -> 52, 将building block 都换成 bottleneck block
52-> 101, 152, 增加了多个 bottleneck block
